snippet.title: Trash Is Fun - Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
Embark on an unforgettable journey around the world in an eco-adventure specially designed for 1-4 players with co-op support. After the apocalypse due to global warming, the characters realized that to survive, they would have to gather in a team and sort and recycle garbage.

Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9mtlz7hmnljb
Microsoft Store: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9pcbc3hq0mvm
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1671310/Trash_is_Fun/

Developer: Martin Teapots
Publisher: Brinemedia

Join the movement, and together, let's turn trash into treasures while having a blast in Trash is Fun!
